TO COMPILE:
make

TO RUN:
./mp1

WIREFRAME MODE:
right click to toggle wireframe mode.  (and see that there are no T junctions)

Source code Included:
mp1.cpp - Contains the main glut and opengl calls used make the window and
	draw the image.
I.cpp - Contains all the vertices and edges of the I and the functions
	used to color and draw it.
heart.cpp - Contains all the vertices of the heart, and the function
	to color and draw it.
